- TRADING TERMINAL:

A terminal you can visit that has randomly generated trades from randomly generated names every day.
Trades are 90% to be same rarity, 5% 1 rarity up 5% 1 rarity below
need to have the card in your collection.
Trades refresh every 24 hours.

Deck check trainers:
trainers that only fight you if you have certain cards in your deck: all clefairys, all fire, etc

timed mode:

time attack, 5 seconds to make each move before the game this end turn